        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Advancing Toward Impact Aid Full Funding Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2027 certain activities under the Impact Aid Program. The program provides funding to local educational agencies that have lost property tax revenue due to the presence of tax-exempt federal property or to those that have experienced increased expenditures due to enrollment of federally connected children (e.g., children living on Indian lands or military bases).</p>]]>
        </text>
